Package: UltimaFlorDoLacio
Title: Random Texts in Portuguese by Famous Authors
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Carlos", "de Moura", , "lcbarrosdemoura@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Each main function is intended to give random quotes from authors who wrote in Portuguese (the user can set the seed). The functions are named after these authors and the quotes were extracted from public repositories.
